org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Interaction

Interface MessageComResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommunicationMedia, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource, SwCommunicationResource, SwInteractionResource, SwResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MessageComResourceImpl

    public interface MessageComResource
extends SwCommunicationResource
    A representation of the model object 'Message Com Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Fixed Message Size
    • Mechanism
    • Message Size Elements
    • Message Queue Capacity Elements
    • Message Queue Policy
    • Send Services
    • Receive Services
    See Also:
    SW_InteractionPackage.getMessageComResource()
